1
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:50,480
I came here to set up a lab

2
00:00:50,480 --> 00:00:52,360
to get hold of rare minerals.

3
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,440
They're crucial to our company,

4
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:55,480
absolutely critical.

5
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:56,840
If I leave now,

6
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:58,120
and Hong Ye finds out,

7
00:00:58,440 --> 00:01:00,280
he'll wipe us out.

8
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,640
When that happens,

9
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,280
the lab and the rare minerals

10
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,560
will be completely lost.

11
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:05,840
All these years of work

12
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:06,840
will be for nothing, won't it?

13
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:08,440
So you've thought it through.

14
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:09,680
Hong Ye

15
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,640
is sly as hell.

16
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,400
And Dawa

17
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:13,520
is ruthless.

18
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,920
It's dangerous for you here.

19
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:16,640
I've thought about that.

20
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,160
As long as you can

21
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,320
keep cooperating,

22
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,800
he won't dare touch me.

23
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,640
So keep working with President Xingyu

24
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,160
and play along with them.

25
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:28,120
If we can hold out for ten days,

26
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,720
I can send someone

27
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,920
to ship the minerals safely back home.

28
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,000
Ten days.

29
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,680
Got it.

30
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:36,960
By the way, Doctor.

31
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:38,160
I also heard something.

32
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:40,000
They brought in truth serum today.

33
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,040
They might use it on you.

34
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:42,720
Don't worry.

35
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,440
Truth serum

36
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,720
is no big deal.

37
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,480
I can handle it.

38
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,280
Wake up.

39
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,080
Where is he?

40
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:11,040
You actually didn't leave.

41
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,040
Leave?

42
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,640
Why would I?

43
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:15,400
General Dawa,

44
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:17,400
coming to see me this late...

45
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,160
You want to share a drink

46
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:19,880
with an old man like me?

47
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,320
Perfect.

48
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,120
I've got some top-shelf liquor here.

49
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,240
Distilled from grain.

50
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:24,920
Tastes great.

51
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,680
Dr. Zhang,

52
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,440
have you changed your mind?

53
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,040
Just practicing a bit.

54
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:43,680
A Di came by,

55
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:44,800
didn't he?

56
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,360
A Di?

57
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,680
Didn't see him.

58
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:49,800
Don't know.

59
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,280
Ten days.

60
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,720
Old Zhang still won't say which route?

61
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,640
No.

62
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:04,680
He's not leaving.

63
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,800
Guess he doesn't want to complicate things.

64
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,760
Dawa must be here.

65
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:35,040
He moves fast.

66
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,800
You just went to Dr. Zhang's, huh?

67
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,120
What do you mean, General Dawa?

68
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,400
Even though we're partners right now,

69
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,880
but in the middle of the night,

70
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,280
barging into a married couple's home

71
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,120
isn't very friendly, is it?

72
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:56,600
President Shen,

73
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,320
Did my useless nephew

74
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,520
bother you again?

75
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,320
Hong Ye,

76
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,480
I really didn't expect

77
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,400
that in less than a day,

78
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:08,400
General Dawa would barge into my company again.

79
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,040
If this keeps up,

80
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,960
should I call for international rescue?

81
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,960
It's a misunderstanding.

82
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,320
Just another misunderstanding.

83
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,520
Dawa.

84
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:18,680
In the middle of the night,

85
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,680
running over to their place again?

86
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,520
Interrupting a young couple's fun?

87
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,680
Get back here. Now.

88
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,920
Got it.

89
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,320
That scared me to death.

90
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,880
Honey,

91
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,960
do you think that bastard Dawa

92
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,160
did it on purpose?

93
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:04,160
Barging in and messing everything up,

94
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,440
completely killed the mood.

95
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,920
Of course he did.

96
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,880
Now that we're working with Hong Ye,

97
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,560
he'll definitely try to sabotage us.

98
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:13,720
Him?

99
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,040
He's a useless piece of trash.

100
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,640
A petty little creep.

101
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,000
Honey,

102
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,040
how about we continue?

103
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,400
Give me a kiss.

104
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,000
Move.

105
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,000
That's enough.

106
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:40,920
We're done.

107
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,480
If only Wu Di were here.

108
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:16,200
Back then, Wu Di was just a security guard.

109
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,320
I barely knew him,

110
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,640
and I dragged him into marrying me.

111
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:23,000
I even called him a coward,

112
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:27,080
said he was too scared to admit he loved me.

113
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:29,400
But back then,

114
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:32,360
he watched over me from across the street.

115
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,480
Even though I couldn't see him,

116
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,200
I knew he was there.

117
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,360
Do you remember this?

118
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:54,040
This is the token

119
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,240
my brother gave you to protect me.

120
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,320
It's also our token of love.

121
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:03,040
I've always kept it with me,

122
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,400
because I feel like as long as it's here,

123
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:11,280
it's like you're right beside me, protecting me.

124
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,360
Wu Di.

125
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,760
Wu Di.

126
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,840
Wu Di!

127
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,720
Protect my sister, Shen Xingyu.

128
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:45,440
Safeguard Wushuang for her.

129
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:48,840
Shen Xingyu!

130
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,520
Xingyu!

131
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:14,760
Xingyu!

132
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,080
Honey...

133
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,600
You get up at 6:50 sharp every day.

134
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:24,920
You like cats,

135
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,720
but you're allergic to their fur.

136
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,600
And the person you love most is me.

137
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,600
My name's Zhao Wudi.

138
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,880
Zhao Wudi.

139
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,920
Wu Di.

140
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:54,920
Xingyu...

141
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,320
Wu Di...

142
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,400
It really is you.

143
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,840
Xingyu...

144
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,040
I'm sorry.

145
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,760
I can't reveal who I am to you right now.

146
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,240
I'm really sorry.

147
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,480
Wait until I finish the mission.

148
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,880
Just hold on a little longer.

149
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:09,080
Uncle,

150
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:11,520
He definitely found the bug.

151
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,360
He insulted me on purpose.

152
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,600
I actually think...

153
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,320
You should be happy about it.

154
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:21,520
The more capable he is...

155
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,400
...the more likely he'll deliver the goods.

156
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,360
The odds of success

157
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,360
are that much higher.

158
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,640
If he didn't have what it takes,

159
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:32,760
I wouldn't trust them either.

160
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:37,840
But I just can't swallow this.

161
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,600
Swallow it whether you want to or not.

162
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:42,440
A little impatience will ruin the big plan.

163
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:44,040
Keep it in your pants.

164
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,760
Once this arms deal goes through,

165
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:47,520
Shen Xingyu

166
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,720
will naturally be yours, won't she?

167
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:49,840
A Di is just

168
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,560
trash who buses plates and dumps slop.

169
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:53,720
Now he's Shen Xingyu's husband, Zhao Wudi.

170
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:55,920
Who the hell is he, really?

171
00:10:58,720 --> 00:10:59,760
Now that you mention it,

172
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,960
I actually had someone look into him.

173
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:07,120
He and the legendary Zhao Wudi

174
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:12,320
really do look exactly alike.

175
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:14,960
I can't figure it out.

176
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,560
I just don't know what he's really after.

177
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,720
As long as this arms deal goes through,

178
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:20,840
why the hell do you care who he is?

179
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,960
Keep a close eye on him.

180
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:26,400
Don't leave his side for a second.

181
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:27,320
Yes.

182
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,320
What are you standing around for?

183
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,120
I'm on it.

184
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:47,560
Master.

185
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:50,680
I picked these nearby.

186
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:51,360
They're for you.

187
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:52,960
Thanks.
